bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6D9D4Dt.jpg&h=5ef3c93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxKsXYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxKsXYs.jpg&h=d2b8d8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多少的相差 會爭執重傷<br />\n好比當一位 戰爭裡遺孀 無非出於勉強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d056a71f719493d3eb188f5ffcefbbc4c96275","tid":2364310,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/he2qKD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhe2qKD2.jpg&h=1c94937e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G126t5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG126t5H.jpg&h=f2948da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mpf7XY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpf7XY3.jpg&h=a047bd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱憾過 也就懂 學會放手的難度<br />\n卻令我 領悟到 愛這東西的深奥 沙律方可偕老"},{"pid":"3e6d6481e9f4c28df64f31c2d9e176077814d559","tid":2364310,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63cx86e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63cx86e.jpg&h=1930e23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSw7dxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSw7dxX.jpg&h=4cd9d1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xF5G2rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxF5G2rn.jpg&h=952b117a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有些愛未開始已經結束<br />\n未牽手已經退縮 未親暱過 但我已經<br />\n再無力繼續<br />\n有些痛未懂得痛都會懂<br />\n未親手抱擁過但我 都猜得透結局<br />\n未有親吻過 未有爭拗過<br />\n未開始相愛都應該結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gi